title: María Paz Azagra
text:
María Paz Azagra Navascues (born 23 August 1982), commonly known as Mari Paz, is a former Spanish <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>. She played for <a href="SD%20Lagunak%20%28women%29">SD Lagunak</a> and <a href="Rayo%20Vallecano%20%28women%29">Rayo Vallecano</a> in Spain's <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20%28women%29">Superliga Femenina</a>, and <a href="Southampton%20Saints%20L.F.C.">Southampton Saints</a> in England's <a href="FA%20Women%27s%20Premier%20League">Premier League</a>.
She was a member of the <a href="Spain%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Spanish national team</a>.
